subtitle: Special Black Friday Discounts
content:
Chase your holiday meal down with a veritable buffet of Black Friday desserts, including some of the highest discounts ever offered on select vehicles below, along with 50% off a portfolio of hot properties — available from November 27 through December 3:

— Mammoth Avenger – 70% off
— Benefactor Terrorbyte – 50% off
— Mammoth F-160 Raiju (Plane) – 40% off
— Imponte Deluxo (Sports Classic) – 40% off
— And more

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for the full list of discounted items.
